e=3D"Gamma ray">gamma rays</a>,<br><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki=
/Beta_particle" title=3D"Beta particle">beta particles</a>, <a href=3D"http=
s://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Muon" title=3D"Muon">muons</a></td>
<td>1
</td></tr>
<tr>
