er/svg/bf5be62d9f63f5df52e8bc156f950d41e131d99f" class=3D"mwe-math-fallback=
-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.838ex; width:4.425ex; height:2.843ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle E(t=
)}"></span> as the sum of the products of the committed organ or tissue equ=
ivalent doses and the appropriate tissue weighting factors <span class=3D"m=
we-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inl=
ine mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://ww=
w.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displaystyle W_{t}}">
  <semantics>
    <mrow class=3D"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD">
